schools.name: Clifford O. Pete Findlay Middle School

data.description: Beautiful & highly upgraded 4 bedroom home with low HOA. Located minutes from excellent schools, shopping and recreational parks. Kitchen features granite countertops, shaker cabinets with under cabinet lighting, pendant lighting over the 8 ft. long island provides open style view into the great room. Excellent for entertaining guest inside. Ceiling fan in every room as well as ceiling speakers in living room, main bedroom and 4th bedroom. 6 security cameras stay with the property. 2 car garage features extra welding plugs, extra lighting and storage. The desert landscaping in front/back yard is very easy to maintain. Backyard is big enough to fit pool and still have room for entertaining. This home is ready to be yours.
